{"tid":328502,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"一人n個超市好食嘅小籠包牌子","createTime":"2017-07-19T15:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T16:21:00.000Z","uid":1858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c66c5e251d3d31c1e2fbc7c6cabe2326f9f025d1","tid":328502,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:28:01.000Z","msg":"以前迷過一排南翔，隔左七年冇食，依家食番覺得好似冇以前咁正，唔知係佢退步左定我以前唔識食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW,搭單問大家知唔知一隻灌湯小籠包／餃（唔記得），同樣都係七年前左右。以前OK有得賣，成10蚊定10幾蚊粒，好似一方盒豆腐花嘅size,，知唔知依家仲有冇得賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc84633f90a424cd565300a50e0d8ce5ecc7d29","tid":328502,"uid":21077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:35:30.000Z","msg":"御品皇果隻點睇，幾多汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8daf4faa177745b19b0a5bcff642cf83fc5543ef","tid":328502,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:44:58.000Z","msg":"南翔, 公仔牌都差晒<br />\n急凍嘅無一隻牌子好食"},{"pid":"02d0056a5ca16d8a25d815898b9161273e71a943","tid":328502,"uid":27680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"快易煮<br />\n我覺得平價黎講幾好食"},{"pid":"3af942353251d752c695566dc3012c8604ac67fe","tid":328502,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431c673b4374fa2b224c972e9eb252bb5897b87e","tid":328502,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:21:00.000Z","msg":"餃子呢"}]}